OK now heres how u make ur own server. First u must have JDK6.0 and winrar. now u need a source so go into th downloads section hit downloads list. i suggest to start out by using testscape. ne ways downlaod testscape then it will bring u to winrar… right click testscape and hit extract to specified folder. then hit desktop and extract it. now it will show on ur desktop so exit out of winrar. go to ur desktop double click testscape and hit compile. Get perfect compiler of mod t’s tut. then hit c to compile. then r to run. congratz u have a server
